S = ServerAPI only
U = UnAuth allowed

GET /v1/players/STEAMID [U]
PUT|PATCH /v1/players/STEAMID [S]

GET /v1/players?start=X&count=Y [U]
  Get best Y players starting at offset X (order by TotalCredits DESC)

GET /v1/applications?faction=FACTION [Check for IsFactionLeader && FACTION == SteamID->Faction]
GET /v1/applications/STEAMID
PUT /v1/applications/STEAMID
DELETE /v1/applications/STEAMID

FUTURE
POST /v1/players/STEAMID/token {ttl} [S]
  Create auth token expiring after <ttl> seconds
 
